'''''Free Bop!''''' is an album by saxophonist [[Charles McPherson (musician)|Charles McPherson]] which was recorded in 1978 and released on the [[Xanadu Records|Xanadu]] label.<ref>[http://www.jazzdiscography.com/Leaders/McPhersonCharles-ldr.php Charles McPherson discography] accessed April 28, 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.jazzlists.com/SJ_Label_Xanadu.htm Xanadu Records discography] accessed April 24, 2014</ref>
