The [[Allmusic]] review awarded the album 4Â½ stars stating "This is perhaps his fiercest, most exciting playing as a leader".<ref name="Allmusic">Wynn, R., [http://www.allmusic.com/album/free-bop!-mw0000879693 Allmusic Review] accessed April 28, 2014</ref>

